review_data: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2019
name: pccoder
title: I wish there was ZERO stars
review: My wife bought me a bunch of yogurts over the weekend, as she usually does.I opened this yogurt up this morning seeing the world "Blackberry" on the label.I should have read closer.It was a shock when I tasted it.Let's get this out of the way immediately.I love jalapenos on my Mexican food.Now, mixed with blackberry...and added to yogurt?That was some of the worst yogurt I've ever had in my life.I do not know who would have thought this is a good combination.Please, if you think I'm wrong go buy yourself some blackberry yogurt, cut up a jalapeno and then mix them together.If you still think it's good then buy some of this.Otherwise steer clear and stick with the other Noosa yogurts that taste so good.
